caption: If you’re already a fan of Toteme, Staud, and The Row, you’ll want to get to know a new wave of neutral palette-loving contemporary designers making waves this season. Labels like Gia Studios, Liberowe, The Garment, and Rohé are redefining modern minimalism with pieces that are simple yet striking, wearable yet statement-worthy. At the link in our bio, shop the 20 contemporary designers filling our wardrobes now.
